            {
              "type": "prose",
              "iaja": "I",
              "text": "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Financials at Triaging are a primer, not a forensic read — the aim is to rule out obvious red flags in cash generation, capex intensity, and balance sheet health before spending further energy. Five years of reported KPIs show revenue compounding at 11% with GP margin widening from 38% to 44%."
            },
