              "type": "prose",
              "iaja": "J",
              "ratings": [
                {
                  "grade": "B",
                  "attr": "financial quality"
                }
              ],
              "text": "Numbers are good enough to proceed. Not outstanding — two of the last five years show working-capital absorption that masked real cash conversion. Worth a closer look at ESA, but no disqualifier at Triaging."
            }
          ]
